    "analysis": "Previous step computed global P95/P5 per (cmdb_id,kpi_name), filtered metric data to the incident window, and counted per-(cmdb,kpi) anomalies. The attempt to summarize consecutive anomaly runs found no precomputed 'runs_top20' (runs_df was empty), so run-length analysis was not yet performed. We still need to determine persistence (consecutive minutes) and severity of high anomalies to identify real faults before moving to traces/logs.",
